---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import { config } from '../config';
---

<Layout title="About" description={`About ${config.author.name}`}>
  <h1>ABOUT</h1>

  <p>
    I’m Jonathan Rhyne — Co-founder &amp; CEO of <a href="https://nutrient.io">Nutrient</a>
    (formerly PSPDFKit). We build document infrastructure for developers and the
    systems they’re now building with AI.
  </p>

  <p>
    I left a law career to build software, started PSPDFKit in 2014, and have spent
    the last decade obsessed with one question: how do you build products people can
    trust when the underlying systems keep changing?
  </p>

  <p>
    These days that means living at the intersection of documents, workflow automation,
    and agentic AI — OCR, extraction, redaction, signatures, orchestration, and the
    accountability layer between model output and real-world decisions.
  </p>

  <p>
    I write about what’s working, what’s hype, and what actually survives production.
    If there’s a recurring theme in my work, it’s this: autonomy can be delegated;
    accountability can’t.
  </p>

  <p>
    Based in Raleigh, NC. Dad. Builder. Soccer, astrophotography, Leica.
  </p>

  <hr />

  <p>
    <a href={config.social.github}>GitHub</a> ·
    <a href={config.social.linkedin}>LinkedIn</a> ·
    <a href={config.social.twitter}>X</a> ·
    <a href={`mailto:${config.social.email}`}>Get in touch</a>
  </p>
</Layout>

<style>
  h1 { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
</style>
